data.description: Great opportunity to buy in Mandeville High School District just seconds away from the Causeway! Completely renovated Acadian style home in the highly sought after Fontainebleau Subdivision right by the Causeway! This gorgeous home is located by the rear entrance of the subdivision and backs up to one of the neighborhood ponds! This 4 bedroom, 3 full bathroom beauty is 2 stories with the primary suite and 1 guest bedroom located downstairs. The entire back wall of the home is lined with windows allowing natural light + views of the lush neighborhood greenery + pond. The vaulted ceilings in the living area, custom ship-lap fireplace + floating shelves are stunning! Owners took down the wall between the kitchen + living area, added a wood beam, 10 ft long island, quartz counters, custom back-splash, wood accents, designer fixtures + appliances- It's a chef's dream kitchen! Primary bathroom remodeled with custom ship-lap, soaking tub, custom tiled shower, double vanities, quartz counters + designer light fixtures! 2 guest bedrooms upstairs have a jack-n-jill style bathroom! Both have huge updated en suite private vanities! Laundry room is through the reclaimed door in the kitchen that also leads out to the attached garage with an AC split! The backyard is fully fenced with gorgeous views of the neighborhood pond. Owner also added a large 360 SQFT covered patio! Backyard additionally has a gazebo, 2 sheds + a storage container. TURN KEY + move in READY! Roof under 5 years old. Mandeville Blue Ribbon Schools! C flood zone.
